{"tid":827052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山竹摧毀駐港解放軍運輸艦「濫交86」","createTime":"2018-09-18T16:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T00:50:30.000Z","uid":5195,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab7f0c2841dd3327d20c86329c7606b5a7dd964","tid":827052,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:09:28.000Z","msg":"山竹蹂躪本港，連解放軍艦船亦遭殃。駐港部隊一艘艦船，在山竹襲港期間被吹至交椅洲擱淺。《蘋果》今午到現場了解，發現遇事的艦船是「南交86」，船身有明顯損毀，船上甲板及附近石灘則有穿海軍軍服的軍人留守，而船隻則用了數條大纜綁緊，以防被沖出大海。本報正向解放軍駐港部隊及海事處查問意外事故，以及有否人受傷等。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，「南交86」是解放軍駐港部隊的軍用交通艇，是42米級側壁式氣墊運輸船，由中船桂江廠製造，在駐港部隊服役多年。駐港部隊的軍艦平日會停泊在昂船洲避風塘內的軍用碼頭，但打風期間，各軍艦要駛出碼頭，到港內的浮筒位置停泊落錨。消息稱，事發於周日中午12時許，當時10號強颱風山竹吹襲本港，「南交86」的鋼錨疑被吹斷，船隻再被吹至交椅洲東面石灘擱淺。海事處事後有接獲報告，但事發兩日後「南交86」仍停在石灘位置。<br />\n<br />\n今日現場所見，約42米長的「南交86」，向海方向的中間船身有明顯被撞毀痕跡，原本密封的船艙，有約10多米外層毀壞，可見船艙內的情況，而船艙及甲板上則有數名軍人，似是在檢查及善後，另外，在岸上亦有兩名身穿海軍軍服的軍人留守。<br />\n<br />\n根據資料，「南交86」於2001年7月24日在颱風玉兔襲港時，停泊在香港维多利亞港B3浮筒時，遭到停泊在附近，懷疑斷錨的「東方公主」輪撞及扣損毀，解放軍駐港部隊其後向有關船公司索償逾20萬元維修費。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180918/large/1537271123_fda8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180918%2Flarge%2F1537271123_fda8.jpg&h=5db34e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180918/large/1537271128_e461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180918%2Flarge%2F1537271128_e461.jpg&h=93f02673&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180918/large/1537271123_497b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180918%2Flarge%2F1537271123_497b.jpg&h=f425f0e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db2cb5799e1e5249f119d77d0e30dc77e8070d84","tid":827052,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:10:26.000Z","msg":"厲害了蟈的船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b01bc21fe665f1573cef736732fea7660aca267","tid":827052,"uid":57543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:11:45.000Z","msg":"不意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fa937953799424fd488d2795999c736074915a","tid":827052,"uid":9564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:12:49.000Z","msg":"颱風都頂唔住仲話打美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdcae3314ac403fd08c3d2494c8077ecb8924882","tid":827052,"uid":113250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:18:09.000Z","msg":"望落似上世紀產物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979d6271074538a562ab02594ab169147ad20fe8","tid":827052,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:23:02.000Z","msg":"漁船黎架下嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a173212306f19ae146669cb46f1f9a5195c64802","tid":827052,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:24:06.000Z","msg":"軍艦都可以咁撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721fb143040de64d4a6891d5cad02c8730df08bd","tid":827052,"uid":175896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:24:53.000Z","msg":"渡海小輪扮軍艦？"},{"pid":"22b348c34316bbb4f22cc3baf77ccb6cbc998657","tid":827052,"uid":10890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T17:38:42.000Z","msg":"之前班解手軍唔係聲大大話要出嚟幫香港救災咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來係冇貨賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm